@startuml state-membership
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontSize 10

title Membership Standing States

[*] --> Active : Onboarding complete\n& first payment succeeds

Active --> Active : Monthly payment\nsucceeds

Active --> Suspended : 3 consecutive\npayment failures

Suspended --> Reinstated : Member updates\npayment method &\noutstanding balance paid

Reinstated --> Active : Next monthly\npayment succeeds

Suspended --> Cancelled : No resolution\nafter 30 days

Cancelled --> [*]

note right of Suspended
  - Cannot submit assistance requests
  - Cannot vote in governance
  - Retains contribution history
  - Receives reinstatement reminders
end note

note right of Reinstated
  - Waiting-period timer restarts
  - Contribution history preserved
end note

@enduml
